#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: sidebar_label
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Theme the portal"
msgstr "Тема портала"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Customize the appearance of the user portal"
msgstr "Настройка внешнего вида портала"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:8
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The portal is customizable from the webadmin:\n"
" `Domains` > Choose a top level domain > `Features`\n"
msgstr ""
"Портал можно настраивать через веб-панель администратора:\n"
" `Domains` > Выберите домен верхнего уровня > `Features`\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Options for the Portal customization"
msgstr "Параметры настройки Портала"

#. type: Title ###
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Show the list of public apps to visitors"
msgstr "Показывать посетителям список общедоступных приложений"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Visitors will see a 'public apps' page when ending up on the portal instead of just the login form.\n"
msgstr ""
"Вместо формы входа на портал посетители увидят страницу «общедоступные "
"приложения».\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Show other domain's apps"
msgstr "Показ приложений других доменов"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "All apps from all domains will be visible on the portal. Default value is `true`.\n"
msgstr ""
"На портале будут отображаться все приложения из всех доменов. Значение по "
"умолчанию — `true`.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Custom title"
msgstr "Пользовательский заголовок"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choose a Title for the Portal\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Custom logo"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choose a image. Accept .svg, .png and .jpeg. Prefer a monochrome .svg with `fill: currentColor` so that the logo adapts to the themes.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Default color theme"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choose a color theme. Users are allowed to choose another one in their settings.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:34
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"* App tiles display theme\n"
"    * simple = display apps icons\n"
"    * descripitive = display apps icons and a descpriction of the application\n"
"    * periodic = display tiles with name apps.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Search engine URL"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "This is an optional feature, allowing to display a search bar in the portal (for example if you like to use your YunoHost portal as your browser's home page). This should be an URL with an empty query string such as `https://duckduckgo.com/?q=, with q=` as duckduckgo's empty query parameter\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Custom user intro"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:42
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can use HTML, basic styles will be applied to generic elements.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "Custom public intro"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "* Custom CSS stylesheet\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/10.theming.mdx:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "This is for advanced admins willing to customize the appearance of the portal.\n"
msgstr ""
